Glad to hear that it's building now! Since the original build problem is fixed, I'm going to close this issue.

It's difficult to guess reasons for poor performance, but I'd recommend that you take a look at the [performance guide](https://www.tensorflow.org/performance/performance_guide), and open a new issue if none of these suggestions help.
